%tr
  %td{:style => "padding: 20px 30px; color: rgb(229, 231, 235); background-color: rgba(63, 114, 175, 0.2); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;color:black;"}
    - if @event.type == 'Potluck'
      %p
        Your Potluck Is Set Up!
      %p
        Dear, #{ @event.recipent_name }

      %p
        Your Chesed Train is ready to go! Here are the details:

      %ul
        %li
          Organizer: #{ @event.owner.name }
        %li
          Recipient: #{ @event.end_date.strftime("%A on %D") }
        %li
          Potluck Link: #{ link_to 'Click here', potluck_url(@event) }
      %p
        You’re helping to create something that truly reflects the heart of our community. Log in anytime to manage or view your Potluck.

      %p
        Warm regards,
        <br>
        The Chesed Train Team

    - else
      %p
        Your Chesed Train Is Set Up!
      %p
        Dear, #{ @event.recipent_name }

      %p
        Your Chesed Train is ready to go! Here are the details:

      %ul
        %li
          Organizer: #{ @event.owner.name }
        %li
          Recipient: #{ @event.recipent_name }
        %li
          Chesed Train Link: #{ link_to 'Click here', chesed_train_url(@event) }
      %p
        You’re helping to create something that truly reflects the heart of our community. Log in anytime to manage or view your Chesed Train.

      %p
        Warm regards,
        <br>
        The Chesed Train Team

